{"tid":1351484,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【警告】小心白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:13:37.000Z","uid":261349,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17409c10f2f8cc35fdd3882ce90ef027586e926e","tid":1351484,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"係，街上係多左人屌政府，屌黑警。甚至好多藍絲都轉軚。我地似乎贏盡左民意。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係咁咩？</span></span><br />\n大家諗諗，到左硬踫硬既時候，呢班人只能夠係後面吶喊助威，就好似中英等國既口交部咁，永遠唔會有實際行動，更唔會出來幫手。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過客永遠係過客</span>，我地既目標應該係，只要呢班看客唔好阻住，係屋企打打輿論就夠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而勝負關鍵在於我地本身。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無人知728會發生咩事，但呢個係考驗和理非既關鍵時候：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">究竟事情演變到有人人自危既時候，你地仲肯唔肯出來？有幾多人肯出來？</span>要知道，黑幫係會尋仇的，可以記住你的樣貌，等個幾月後忽然拿刀斬你。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我講講後果，如果無人敢出來，則勇武兄弟會置於死地，運動無疾而終。</span>白色恐怖將令所有人三緘其口，相信西環所打既就係咁既如意算盤！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後，勇武是劍，和理非是盾，希望各位明白其真意。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0482d27d4e7803329a145a2d6ff8ea170b7c347","tid":1351484,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2979d4de797741eeb3868b53ff1bf5cd6d55012a","tid":1351484,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afcb5ae9cfdb76857c041d066a43c77d14ce4408","tid":1351484,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d29113d47e0adc6093aaac2a45189ab07ce77d8","tid":1351484,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:55:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c95f12fc48d3c8e0c823329f4813484df8082d2","tid":1351484,"uid":261349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:04:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90825a2ee936c915f5ab50bc857087b41980c1b1","tid":1351484,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"486256500f10571887898151cec02194b84d213a","tid":1351484,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:13:10.000Z","msg":"【沙盤推演】元朗黑社會襲擊目的與未來佈局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347917</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef059261381268cbe2d09cf714b039e25eb11e02","tid":1351484,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}